{
  "stem": "21089.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to-- oh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to-- the payment was also unusual.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Half of them, I had to pay in Wilno, in Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And other half, I had-- I had only half of the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The other half was stolen in a half.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we came to the-- to the place, I gave him the--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other half.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was torn to half.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No he has the half.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My friend in Lutsk has the other half, and he's supposed to pay him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only signs that he-- that I am over there was-- was no correspondence, was no communications.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when he got the other half, he knew that--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember how much was it, how many rubles or it was, so he brought-- so I-- when I was already leaving, I gave him that.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he actually, he brought me to the street because I didn't know where it is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that time, you have to be careful also because the Lithuanian police was very, very, very tough on the people who illegally-- they knew many people from the Russian territories want to come, illegally immigrated.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And but this was January 1st.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a new year, cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When you walk on the street, it was like kr-ch-ch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Very, very-- never in my life I saw cold weather like that over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I came to Vilna, and I knew already where, where-- over there, some many friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And eventually I registered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- later they regis-- I registered as a-- that I deserted Russian territory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They have special-- but I couldn't work there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Legally, I couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I registered a police as a-- as a illegally immigr-- as illegal immigrant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many people were like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
